::Prowl::

He had been flying over head, recovering for the fight with Megatron and
Firestrike, when he spotted Alpha Dolphy. He flew down to her, and
picked her up.
"Hold on..."
He took off for the base again, but he would have to pass Megatron and
the others to get there.
